Method Detail

isRead

public boolean isRead()
Initially set to false, this property reflects whether or not the session confirmation number has already been read for the current session. The session confirmation number can only be read once per session, usually at login.

Returns:
true if the value has been read for the current session, false otherwise

getSessionConfirmationNumber

public long getSessionConfirmationNumber()
Returns the session confirmation number

Returns:
the session confirmation number
Throws:
java.lang.IllegalStateException - if the session confirmation number has already been read for the current session
